Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:06.03,INlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}誰が気付けただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:13.16,INlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}光の向こうで濃くなる影に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:19.17,INlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}過去が遠くで叫んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:25.13,INlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}背中向けては　耳を塞いでる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:31.35,INlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}すぐ泣くからって弱いと決めないで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:37.81,INlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}泣かないからって強いと思わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:43.69,INlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}君が握る手　暖かさを
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:49.70,INlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}信じてみてもいいかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:56.87,INlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}やっと気付いた　ようやく見つけた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:09:03.17,INlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}涙でぼやけた真実
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:09.38,INlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}僕は僕でいいと　頭を撫でながら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:15.68,INlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}眠る君の　横顔が今
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:22.69,INlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}新しい気持ちを　照らした
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:27.61,INlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ありがとう　そばにいてくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:35.24,INlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}芽吹いたよ　始まりの種が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-----INlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:06.03,INlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}有誰注意到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:13.16,INlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}在光芒的另一側  那漸漸變深的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:19.17,INlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}過去也在遠處嘶吼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:25.13,INlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我轉過身去  摀住了耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:31.35,INlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不要因為愛哭就承認自己軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:37.81,INlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}也別以為從不哭泣的人就很堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:43.69,INlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}你緊握著我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:49.70,INlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我可以相信這份溫暖嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:56.87,INlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}總算察覺到了  終於發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:09:03.17,INlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}被淚水模糊了的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:09.38,INlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}你摸著我的頭  鼓勵我做真實的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:15.68,INlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}你沉睡時的側臉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:22.69,INlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}照亮了我嶄新的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:27.61,INlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}感謝你能伴我左右
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:35.24,INlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}新生的種子  已悄然發芽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-----TXT-----
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:05.05,tuduku,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(556,353)}未完待續
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.23,0:00:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,爆裂吧…現實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,崩斷吧…神經
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,0:00:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(299,328)}Vanishment  this  world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,0:00:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,消失吧  這個世界！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,328)}Avalon  Smasher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,阿瓦隆粉碎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這種無聊的事情你準備做到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.91,0:00:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,很開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一直像個小孩子似的任性下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:00:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,很開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,328)}Gun  twinkle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真眼閃擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你恨媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.03,0:01:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你這麼想讓爺爺奶奶為難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.57,0:01:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你其實也明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.76,0:01:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這是無可奈何的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我們無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.74,0:01:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎麼做你才會滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,無可奈何的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,328)}Evil  Eye
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,邪眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:01:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡已經沒有我們的家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不可視境界線什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不可視境界線是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我認為十花小姐說得很對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但我覺得  正因為知道這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,正因為知道這一點  六花才這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因為是現實就必須得接受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,即使他人這麼說  還是會有很多難以承受的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  事情接連發生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,連調整自己內心的時間都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一切就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不是在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒有打算去無視
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  以理所當然的理由接受理所當然的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  大家說這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,都說現實就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣真的就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都是這麼活著的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是所謂的成長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  六花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才坐計程車回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是去海邊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,在她回來之前  大家去海邊放煙火了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,終於迎來解放暗黑龍的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,慢…慢著！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你在鬧什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,來來來  要丟了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看我丟~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這個好好玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不過話說回來  富樫君和六花好慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,暑假來到海邊後  兩人悄悄出門…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是去邂逅平行世界的戰士了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  富樫君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:06:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,六花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,沒來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,富樫君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真是青春洋溢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說是修羅場？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,修羅場是強力的結界魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的  差點沒趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我要說的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那個地方管理局的力量果然強大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,結界的力量太強了  只好撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說要回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(368,328)}Dark  Flame
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太是從哪裡獲得了漆黑烈焰的力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,都說了那種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一開始只是朋友們說說而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然大家都鬧著一起去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我例外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺有點不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,有一種違和感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,或者說是浮離於這個世界一般奇妙的孤獨感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你是說黑暗的意識喚醒了其他世界的記憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,曾經也有過這樣的感覺吧  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好想忘掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,管理局的干擾？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我說  你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,視線對上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來  我們就締結了更為高等的契約
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,328)}Dark  Flame  Master
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,漆黑烈焰使
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,隨你怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,「被漆黑烈焰吞噬…」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,別鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  是富樫君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,說是小鳥遊同學要回家  去送她了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,還真是大膽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,大膽是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你啊  裝純也得適可而止哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你有和男生交往過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,當然有啦  幼稚園的時候和同班的小孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是之後因為父親工作的原因去了外國
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,小學和國中基本沒上過  一直是請家教輔導
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙  是罕見的正牌天然嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚哇  痛徹全身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,凸守的身體就好像伊卡洛斯的翅膀一樣被太陽灼傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼啦  我想這麼難得的機會  給你搓搓背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,正好有個上好的絲瓜布在手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不要客氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,別靠近我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
